ENTERPRISE FEATURES
-------------------

The following features are designated as Enterprise Edition and require a
valid commercial licence to use in production:

  - SAML 2.0 SSO with per-organisation IdP configuration
  - SCIM 2.0 automated user provisioning
  - Custom roles beyond the four system roles
  - Extended audit log retention (beyond 90 days)
  - Compliance data export (SOC 2, ISO 27001)
  - White-labelling and custom branding
  - Advanced cross-project automation rules
  - Priority support with guaranteed SLA


