COMMUNITY EDITION
-----------------

If you do not hold an Enterprise licence, you may use Boardupscale under
the terms of the AGPL-3.0 (see LICENSE). All core project management
features — including issue tracking, Scrum/Kanban boards, sprint
management, time tracking, GitHub integration, webhooks, API access,
RBAC, and 2FA — are fully available under the Community Edition at no
cost.

Setting ENTERPRISE_ENABLED=false (the default) ensures you run only
Community Edition features.


